    "chapter_title": {
      "en": "The Ninety-Fifth Assembly, the Assembly of Wednesday, Twelve Nights Remain From Sha`ban, 368 AH. Dictated in the Mashhad of Imam al-Rida (s)."
    },
    "nav": {
      "next": "/books/al-amali-saduq:94:5",
